sequenceDiagram
participant User
participant API
participant BusinessLogic
participant Database

User->>API: POST /reviews
API->>BusinessLogic: validate review data

alt invalid review or place not found
    BusinessLogic-->>API: error
    API-->>User: 400 Bad Request
else valid review
    BusinessLogic->>Database: save review
    Database-->>BusinessLogic: review saved
    BusinessLogic-->>API: success
    API-->>User: 201 Created
end
